Bruce Chiu's Arnis Drills - iPod

DVD Rip to iPod

Producer: Bruce Chiu

This DVD will cover Modern Arnis Drills for beginner to advanced martial artists. You will learn the 12 basic strikes of Modern Arnis, Single, Double, Reverse Siniwalli and empty hand applications for each. Also covered are Abanico Drills, the 3-8-12 Drill, 3-8-5-12-12 Drill, 2-2-2 Drill and Defense techniques. Disarms and Strikes are taught both right and left handed and also empty handed.
All  Drills are demonstrated both static and with movement.

Show someone you love them, hit'em with a stick! 

